{"tid":1120799,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重病入院   鄭若驊丈夫潘樂陶僭建罪名成立 罰款2萬元","createTime":"2019-04-23T02:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T08:03:10.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c43a78ec32cbfa427eb462c06dcd411a285b3eed","tid":1120799,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T02:36:06.000Z","msg":"律政司司長鄭若驊丈夫潘樂陶，涉嫌在其位於屯門小欖的獨立屋中僭建逾14立方米的水池，被屋宇署票控。裁判官今早在西九龍裁判法院裁定潘樂陶僭建罪名成立。潘樂陶被判罰款2萬元，須於2周內支付。<br />\n<br />\n辯方透露，潘樂陶昨晚因重病入院，今早未能出庭。<br />\n<br />\n現年78歲的潘樂陶被控於2017年4月2日至2018年1月9日，身為屯門小欖樂翠街海詩別墅三號屋的擁有人，明知未事先獲得建築事務監督的書面批准及書面同意，便在上述處所展開或進行建築工程，即建造一個水池構築物，違反《建築物條例》第14(1)條及40(1AA)條。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190423/_2019042309273253260.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190423%2F_2019042309273253260.jpg&h=282d52e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1484895/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1484895%2F&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0kt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=8efc9f9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1484895%2F&h=debe3bad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1484895/</a>"},{"pid":"aab770de6aaf0bb497c6c82032a7a7408888bd16","tid":1120799,"uid":122233,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T02:41:22.000Z","msg":"獲毛主席接見未"},{"pid":"22d23602fbe3edca613c4c56af82620152a48965","tid":1120799,"uid":60057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"罰兩萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拆都唔止呢個數"},{"pid":"d147e8442ef49739855120699c1ed1cf006aeb9f","tid":1120799,"uid":216760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"有冇人